---
title: Chicken and Butternut Squash Tagine with couscous and sprinkled almonds
description: A tagine is a North African dish, the name of which originally refers to the type of pot in which it's traditionally cooked. This tagine is flavoured with harissa paste and filled which delicious chunks of chicken and tender butternut squash.
